+
+// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
+// P2 — a present-but-NON-STRING timestamp hard-rejects (pre-existing fail-open)
+// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
+
+/// **This fail-open predates the TC-33 migration.** The parse site reads
+/// `edge.get("t_invalid").and_then(|v| v.as_str())`, and `as_str()` returns
